highlights.text: Vũ. has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “bình yên” is the highest at #26.
“Âm Thầm Bên Em” by Sơn Tùng M-TP has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 1739 days straight.

“ĐỘC NHẤT VÔ NHỊ” by ANH TRAI "SAY HI", Karik, Vũ Cát Tường, Gill, Tez, buitruonglinh, Otis, Negav, Mason Nguyen, Sơn.K, CONGB, Jey B, Ngô Kiến Huy, VƯƠNG BÌNH, Nhâm Phương Nam, and Đỗ Nam Sơn is the highest new entry on Top Songs Vietnam at #122.
“Dù Cho Mai Về Sau” by buitruonglinh is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 72 spots at #95.
